You're not alone man this is more common than you think. Once you find your purpose, you'll never be tempted to watch porn or touch yourself ever again. I've been on no fap for a while and honestly I feel more confident in myself. Think of it this way:

Pain now, pleasure later

OR

Pleasure now, pain later

You need to go through the pain of withdrawals of the things you're addicted to in order to feel everlasting pleasure in your life. Or you can bask in the quick pleasure fixes then feel like crap afterwards. It's a paradox, a damn true one.
